# Web Guide - {{ project_name }}

## Tech Stack

- **Next.js** (App Router) with **TypeScript**
- **Tailwind CSS** for styling
- **Axios** for API calls
- **React Context** for auth state
- **Cloudflare Pages** for hosting

## Project Structure

```
web/src/
  app/
    layout.tsx              # Root layout (ThemeProvider, fonts)
    globals.css             # Tailwind base + design token CSS vars
    error.tsx               # Root error boundary
    (auth)/
      login/page.tsx        # Login page (OAuth + optional password)
      register/page.tsx     # Registration page
      layout.tsx            # Centered auth layout
    (main)/
      layout.tsx            # Authenticated layout with navbar
      dashboard/page.tsx    # Dashboard
      examples/
        page.tsx            # List view
        [id]/page.tsx       # Detail view
  lib/
    api/
      client.ts             # Axios instance with auth interceptor
      auth.ts               # Auth API functions
      examples.ts           # Example CRUD functions
    auth/
      context.tsx            # AuthContext + AuthProvider
      guard.tsx              # ProtectedRoute component
      hooks.ts               # useAuth, useUser hooks
    hooks/
      use-api.ts             # Generic data fetching hook
  components/
    ui/                      # Button, Input, Card, etc.
    layout/                  # Navbar, Footer
  types/
    api.ts                   # TypeScript types matching OpenAPI
```

## Conventions

- **App Router** route groups: `(auth)` for public, `(main)` for authenticated
- Axios client auto-attaches Bearer token from localStorage
- 401 responses redirect to `/login`
- Design tokens from `shared/design-tokens/tokens.json` mapped to CSS custom properties
- Server components by default, `'use client'` only when needed

## Commands

```bash
task web:dev      # npm run dev (port 3000)
task web:build    # npm run build
task web:lint     # npm run lint
task web:test     # npm run test
task web:deploy   # npx wrangler pages deploy
```
